01:33:31,690 --> 01:33:35,069
♪ Massive paws, killer
claws for the feast ♪

1567
01:33:35,178 --> 01:33:37,023
♪ Hear him roar, see him roam ♪

1568
01:33:37,101 --> 01:33:40,319
♪ But we're not coming home
