(GROANS)

1660
01:37:46,629 --> 01:37:47,785
Gaston!

1661
01:37:51,774 --> 01:37:52,836
Gaston!

1662
01:37:53,157 --> 01:37:54,255
Help me.

1663
01:37:54,344 --> 01:37:55,664
Sorry, old friend.

1664
01:37:56,064 --> 01:37:57,610
It's hero time.

1665
