(ROARS)

1779
01:44:43,093 --> 01:44:44,514
(WHIMPERS)

1780
01:44:44,614 --> 01:44:47,801
(SCREAMING)

1781
01:44:53,791 --> 01:44:55,940
(THE BEAST BREATHING HEAVILY)

1782
01:45:00,450 --> 01:45:01,978
You came back.

1783
