1789
01:45:15,440 --> 01:45:17,310
One last time.

1790
01:45:20,284 --> 01:45:22,057
(BREATHES SHAKILY)

1791
01:45:22,424 --> 01:45:23,596
No!

1792
01:45:23,673 --> 01:45:25,142
